high_descs: Step forward, then turn right to go to the dresser.
Pick up the computer on the dresser, in front of the statue.
Turn right, then go forward to go toward the lamp.
Turn on the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Examine a computer in the lamp light.

high_descs: Walk to the laptop computer on the tall brown dresser.
Close the laptop and pick it up.
Turn right and walk to the white sofa.
Look up and turn on the standing lamp next to the sofa.
anns.task_desc: Turn on the lamp next to the sofa while holding a laptop computer.

high_descs: Turn right towards the dresser with the laptop.
Close the lid of the laptop on the dresser and pick up the laptop.
Turn right and walk towards the white sofa.
Raise the laptop up and turn on the lamp on the left.
anns.task_desc: Examine a laptop by the light of a tall lamp.

high_descs: Turn to the right and move across the room to face the dresser.
Close the lid of the laptop and pick it up.
Turn to the right and move towards the white couch.
Turn on the lamp next to the couch.
anns.task_desc: Examine a laptop by the light of a lamp.

high_descs: Turn to your right walk towards the cabinet
Pick up the laptop on the cabinet
Turn to your right walk straight to the lamp on your left beside the sofa
Turn on the lamp
anns.task_desc: Examine the laptop by the light

high_descs: turn right, walk forward to the dresser
close the computer that is on the dresser, pick up the computer
turn right, walk forward to the couch, lift computer up to the lamp
turn the lamp on
anns.task_desc: examine a computer with a lamp
